values: Man I had a good weekend!!  Friday I went to school and I thought I wasgonna go home then Rose was gonna come pick me up, but when I got to 3rd she was there so I called my mom and after school I went to Rosa Brito's house.  This girl, Jamie Bennet, and this guy, Stephen, went with us.  Well we, Stephen, Rosa, and me, dropped Jamie off at her house then went to Rosa's.  Rosa changed then we all went to Jamie's and there was 50 kids well there was really like 10!!  So we stayed there and helped with the kids, died Stephen's hair, my mom brought my clothes, then we left!!  First we had to go get MiMi from Adam McFall's house and my friend Denver was the one driving!!  So we went and got her and we went to the store and got 2 12 packs of budlight and a 12 pack of Smirnoff tribleblack and went to the party at Jasons well we sat out said soo long then they got there and I was on like my 10th beer lol.  But someone stole some weed from Jason and everyone had to leave!!  then Saturday I went to the Beach and now I have a cold and Im sun burnt lol well bye.

hey everyone well I'm pretty sure I failed my Math FCAT today, it is sooo hard!!  But I got to drive my car when I got home today!!  I didn't ride the bus today either, I rode with Olivia and we had to drop off a applacation at Texas Roadhouse then we went to Fred's, gees she is soooo picky!!  It was horrible shopping with her!!  Plus I didn't have any money!!  so yea I'll probably write later cause when my step-daddy gets home he pisses me off soo I'll need to write about it!! lol well bye bye
<3 Always,
Mallory

Well today was good, I went to school and took my FCAT I think I passed it, it was pretty easy!!  Anyways, after school I went to Donna's and just hung out there for a while!!  Man, I hate little kids!!!  Emily, Donna's niece, is soo mean she doesn't listen to ANYONE and she pissed me OFF!!  When I was there she was like "Mallory I seen you smoking at the movies" and I was like "I wasn't smoking I was holding it for someone"  then she said "Well that doesn't matter I know you smoke" and I said "Larry PLEASE make her go take a bath!" lol  But yea I hate it.  Man if those stupid fucks would have talked to me today I would have jacked a jaw lol I hate them!!  Ok there's these stupid people that live next to Donna and the guy that lives there HIT my 75 year old grandpa soo if I ever fucking see that piece of shit out side then I'll fucking beat the shit out of him!! Well I have to go cause I don't know what else to talk about so I'll write LATER!!

I'm soo fun!!lol  Anyways today I went to school then when i got off the bus I went to my "cousins" Olivia's house, then to Donna's!!  Man I've never been so inparssed!!  Larry, Donna's sisters boyfriend, was picking on me THEN his brother, Chad, came over and Larry started breaking out the stories Man that was BAD!!  lol Even though everyone else thought they were funny I didn't, He was talking about this time when I was all like "I really need a job" he said "well my friend Ben (sitting in the chair right there) will give you a job planting tulips" and I got all excited then like a month later Donna and I were talking and I was telling her about the "job" and she started laughing and I was like "What are you laughing about??"  Then she said "he didn't mean tulips he meant Two Lips" lol and I was sooo dumb why cant I figure this stupid shit out?? Anyways I got to go so I can talk to this really cute guy and maybe hang out with him soo I'll write later!!
                             <3 Always,
                             Mallory

Man I'm soo mad ..... There is this guy that I like and he is such a ass, he came to my house, we talked on the phone, he said that he liked me, but now he wont even talk to me on the internet!!!  I don't know if I should even worry about it, probably not but, I do like him and now he wont talk to me!!  I hate stupid assholes!!

This is soo fun I think I might like everyone knowing what I do all the time lol!!  Anyways I think I had a good day except this morning when my mom was being a meanie lol ..... yea anyways I'm gonna go cause I don't really have anything else to write about soo I'll write tomorrow!!  ohh thanks Ryan and Donna love you guys!!

                                 <3 Always,
                                 Mallory
